{"tid":698843,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"食評：九龍城 Futurus Gourmet","createTime":"2018-06-12T05:09:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-14T13:23:36.000Z","uid":181719,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"67522c74c75936b51323d5466fcf610a86259219","tid":698843,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T05:09:50.000Z","msg":"上次去chicken n egg，途中發現呢間好有私房菜feel嘅野，專賣parma ham嘅，但有set dinner食，168起，感覺間野有好強嘅氣，話比我聽佢係好食嘅，一定要試下。<br />\n<br />\n然後喺超過35度嘅某一晚，由樂富站行到去佢門口，先發現我想食嘅牛扒係168+90再加一，長期糧尾黎講，真係有啲想走，但係實在太熱喇，都係入去豪多餐。<br />\n<br />\n經過凍櫃位，原來入面別有洞天，梳化位超闊落好坐。最重要係，又係包場！一個客都冇！真係瞓喺度食都得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/125324_499e6acaf6140de482d1f3fd63e59550.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F125324_499e6acaf6140de482d1f3fd63e59550.jpeg&h=ebec77b7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/125331_a3cdaa93874616e3a1ff0b2445bc9a1a.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F125331_a3cdaa93874616e3a1ff0b2445bc9a1a.jpeg&h=f4353017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n為咗平啲，2個人嗌咗一個牛扒set加一碟雞翼。<br />\n<br />\n雞翼食落似係烤焗做法，外面金黃色一點點，味道似係咸蛋黃整出黎嘅醬咁，但又唔太咸，算烤得幾好食。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/125344_97dae5e8bd5d6b8304f806c59d98b003.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F125344_97dae5e8bd5d6b8304f806c59d98b003.jpeg&h=0d031178&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nset dinner個湯不過不失，冇乜特別。之後上個頭盤係沙樂美腸多士，就幾驚喜，驚喜在舊麵包好鬆軟，配塊薄薄嘅腸片係恰到好處 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/125353_aa041c9f47d092e77a98d9a3e59aec15.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F125353_aa041c9f47d092e77a98d9a3e59aec15.jpeg&h=96cb1ff8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/125401_88cce3615a347f79f98e07233f0f5da3.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F125401_88cce3615a347f79f98e07233f0f5da3.jpeg&h=88b4b213&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但最驚喜嘅都係塊牛扒，餐牌寫出黎好似係安格斯，以1蚊1g黎講，佢份量真係有168+90咁大塊，肉汁真係豐富，肉味真係香濃，只係落咗少少粗鹽吊味，口感已經相當好 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 粗薯條亦都係水準之作，如果有埋啤酒送就完美喇，所以雖然間野好好坐，但食完之後都係好快上埋蘋果批（個批就好一般），埋單出去飲酒。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/125414_b944f5421c55ccbb033e77d25fd0b5e7.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F125414_b944f5421c55ccbb033e77d25fd0b5e7.jpeg&h=b92c80cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/12/125420_286d287f9cbe2970300a2ca0af9f3c80.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F12%2F125420_286d287f9cbe2970300a2ca0af9f3c80.jpeg&h=77043a66&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c54aa00a3677270e9417aafb671d035a57702ee8","tid":698843,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:49:19.000Z","msg":"冇人講野 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51636e7cfbb8eeaf807188138dd8c89224576b5","tid":698843,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:57:56.000Z","msg":"兩個人點夠飽。<br />\n<br />\n牛排個樣有啲普通。"},{"pid":"dfc0aabe400693591960b6f6f0de6312c1ea30fa","tid":698843,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"帥呆了"},{"pid":"6dc87705f42b804a2245275ddde3bf125ea26826","tid":698843,"uid":181719,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d51636e7cfbb8eeaf807188138dd8c89224576b5","tid":698843,"uid":2442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T14:57:56.000Z","msg":"兩個人點夠飽。<br />\n<br />\n牛排個樣有啲普通。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T16:29:21.000Z","msg":"唔夠架，慳錢嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食完去買啤酒飲飽咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a41aaa7138e5c2c3edcdc8bb70267dbef95a2b0","tid":698843,"uid":181719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfc0aabe400693591960b6f6f0de6312c1ea30fa","tid":698843,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"帥呆了"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T16:29:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b2b959ebc84c40978a42bfb647851c0de155f6b","tid":698843,"uid":179814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T12:31:38.000Z","msg":"樓主放咗上OpenRice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95bd660c71814ac7c88b7740440e3c045feea26a","tid":698843,"uid":181719,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4b2b959ebc84c40978a42bfb647851c0de155f6b","tid":698843,"uid":179814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T12:31:38.000Z","msg":"樓主放咗上OpenRice<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T13:23:36.000Z","msg":"梗係一稿n投咁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}